href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> 接口的 <code><strong>controllers</strong></code> 属性返回 chorme 窗口的 XUL 控制器。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>controllers</var> = <em>window</em>.controllers\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>controllers</code> 是一个类型为 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XULControllers\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>XULControllers</code></a>（<a href=\"/en-US/docs/XPCOM_Interface_Reference/nsIControllers\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>nsIControllers</code></a>）的对象。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<p>XUL-专有属性，不属于任何规范。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p>默认情况下，窗口的控制器包含支持全局窗口命令的代码。</p>\n\n<p>chrome 代码可以添加控制器（与 globalOverlay.js 中的 <code>goDoCommand</code> 和 <code>goUpdateCommand</code> 函数配合使用）。</p>\n\n<p>然而，浏览器窗口被关闭时，我们必须手动删除这些添加的控制器，因为浏览器并不会自动完成这些操作。</p>\n\n<p>如果有忘记删除的控制器，则会导致错误：</p>\n<a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=415775\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 415775</a>:\n\n<pre class=\"bz_comment_text notranslate\" id=\"comment_text_0\">ASSERTION: XPConnect is being called on a scope without a 'Components' property!</pre>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"Window 接口的 controllers 属性返回 chorme 窗口的 XUL 控制器。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.controllers","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.controllers","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"window.controllers","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/controllers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/controllers/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/controllers","title":"Window.controllers"}],"pageTitle":"Window.controllers - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}